  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether nasal intubation assisted by GlideScope
      videolaryngoscopy is faster, easier, and less traumatic than nasal intubation with
      conventional direct laryngoscopy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
